data.description: This remarkable historic home in Independence has been freshly and fully remodeled in 2015, including new electrical and plumbing (the sewer line was also replaced in 2018). Newer kitchen, bathrooms, roof, ductless heating and cooling, water heater, the list goes on, with 5 large bedrooms also with Cadets, a full RV pad out front, and alleyway parking to allow for views of the neighborhood on your enclosed front porch including a swing. The sprinklers were partially installed.
